      "writtenOn": "2016-02-12T17:20:23Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Will do. The reason I called it SystemResult was because it always irked me that these things are called Errors when in fact they also signal success. So you see weird constants like ERROR_SUCCESS. To me it signals the result of an operation, to assume that it\u0027s always an error seems very pessimistic :)",
