      "writtenOn": "2016-02-12T17:20:23Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Initially I didn\u0027t have the from* methods so that\u0027s why Type was public. But with those in place it\u0027s probably a good idea to make Type private as well as the constructor.\n\nResultT was public because I intended to have a get() method that returns the raw code in case someone wants to show it to a user or put it in a log. Seems I forgot to add that method though.",
